&s;ent this tragedy to him, with a &s;hort copy of
<NOTE N="&Dagger;" PLACE="foot">Vol. II. p. 181.</NOTE><NOTE N="&Dagger;" PLACE="foot">Ibid. p. 150.</NOTE>ver&s;es, in which he de&s;ired his correction. Mr. Hill,
