<DIV4 TYPE="scene">
<HEAD>SCENE, Don Philip's apartment
in the governor's hou&s;e.</HEAD>
<STAGE>Enter A&s;pin, Fidelia, and Leonora V$IL'D.</STAGE>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>A&s;p.</SPEAKER>
<P>So, this is the fir&s;t time that ever I turn'd
gentleman-u&s;her&mdash;Methinks I make a notable figure
in my preferment&mdash;Nay, I don't know, but I
may ri&s;e to be a great man.</P>
</SP>
<STAGE>[A&s;ide.</STAGE>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Leo.</SPEAKER>
<P>The creature look, as if he was in love with
him&s;elf&mdash;Hark'e, fellow, where have you brought
us?</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>A&s;p.</SPEAKER>
<P>Not a jo$ from your own inclination, I &s;up|po&s;e
&mdash;Look'e, Madam, it is ma&s;ter', bu&s;ine&s;s to
an&s;wer your que&s;tions&mdash;Here my &s;ervice is at end&mdash;
Methinks, I begin to have a jantee air already&mdash;
I'll &s;ee how I can compliment [<HI>A&s;id$.</HI>].&mdash;Ladies,
I am your mo&s;t humble &s;ervant, and &s;o I take my
