</SP>
<STAGE>[Exit.</STAGE>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Fide.</SPEAKER>
<P>I never &s;aw &s;uch a $word$ in my life!</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<PB N="97" REF="217">
<SPEAKER>Leo.</SPEAKER>
<P>Now we may venture to UNVEIL&mdash;for I
know not where we are, by rea&s;on I never look$d
$word$ of the chair.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Fide.</SPEAKER>
<P>Perhaps Sir Charles may have provided
us one of his mi&s;tre&s;'s apar$ments&mdash;for I know
not what to think of him, now he's grown to in|con&s;tant.</P>
</SP>
